{
  "stem": "833.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We never-- and-- and we were paid by the page, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I did a lot of work there besides to earn some money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And Orgun Sandor then started also teaching in the conservatory in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was one week in Vienna, two weeks in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he must have had a student who couldn't-- I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Who couldn't write anything well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so in many ways, he-- I started composing for somebody whom I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That was a bit better paid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so I composed all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He would call me in the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Well, usually, it was Tuesday morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He called me up and said, Herbert, I need a string quartet, last movement, rondo form, 6/8.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he told me all the-- what the-- the prescription-- and not later than Saturday, 4 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I sat down and wrote a nice, moving string quartet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was after that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was way afterwards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was already at-- at-- towards the end of the '20s.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were the '20s in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, to explain what the '20s were-- it's very difficult because this was a real revolutionary time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I grew up at that time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I matured, in what we call today-- we call it-- of course, we called it at that time Red Vienna.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See, Austria was a peculiar country.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Austrian Vienna was vast majority Social Democrat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was my-- the hinterland of Austria was mostly what is called Christian Social.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That means the dominant force there was the Catholic Church.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Vienna, it was not the Catholic Church.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Vienna, it was the-- the city hall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the city hall was meant by some very, very exciting people, especially two what we call today [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
